<b>Want to customize Magento to fully meet the needs of your business?</b><BR />TBT Corp. is now accepting RFQs for custom Magento projects.  Send me a PM or e-mail for more information about our quality solutions.

<h3>Features</h3><b>Mass Relating Products</b>: One-way relate, multi-relate, or un-relate
<b>Mass Cross-selling Products</b>: Mass cross-selling products: One-way cross-sell, multi-cross-sell, or un-cross-sell
<b>Mass Up-selling Products</b>: One-way up-sell, un-up-sell
<b><a href="http://www.magentocommerce.com/extension/748/enhanced-product-grid">Enhanced Grid</a></b>: This extension requires the Enhanced Grid extension to be installed , which comes with an selection of it's own great features!

<h3>Installation Instructions</h3>YOU MUST INSTALL OR UPDATE TO VERSION 1.04 OR HIGHER OF <a href="http://www.magentocommerce.com/extension/748/enhanced-product-grid">ENHANCED GRID</a> FIRST!
Once you have Enhanced Grid installed, this module should be plug and play. 
<b>Make sure you clear your cache.  Logging in and logging back out may also be required.</b>

